{
  "info": {
    "name": "WHMAZ Reseller REST API (v1)",
    "_postman_id": "b6b2e9a1-4c8f-47e2-9c1a-whmazapi0001",
    "description": "Third-party REST API for WHMAZ CRM resellers.\n\n## Auth\nEvery request sends two headers:\n- `X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}`\n- `X-Api-Secret: {{api_secret}}`\n(or `Authorization: Bearer <key_id>:<secret>`).\n\nCreate a key under **Admin → Settings → API Keys**; the secret is shown once.\n\n## Setup\nEdit the collection variables: `base_url` (e.g. `https://yourdomain.com/api/v1`), `api_key`, `api_secret`, and the sample ids.\n\n## Placing an order\nOrder placement reuses the storefront cart/checkout code. Build a cart (`/cart/add_*`, `/cart/link_*`), then `POST /checkout`, then `POST /invoices/pay/{uuid}` to pay + provision. Pricing ids come from `/products/hosting` (`product_service_pricing_id`), `/products/software` (`software_pricing_id`) and `/domains/check` or `/domains/suggest` (`dom_pricing_id`). Pass `customer_id` to act for a sub-customer (omit to act as the reseller).\n\nResponse envelope: `{ \"success\": true, \"data\": {...} }` or `{ \"success\": false, \"error\": { \"code\": \"...\", \"message\": \"...\" } }`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "https://yourdomain.com/api/v1" },
    { "key": "api_key", "value": "wk_replace_me" },
    { "key": "api_secret", "value": "ws_replace_me" },
    { "key": "customer_id", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "domain_id", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "service_id", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "order_id", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "invoice_uuid", "value": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" },
    { "key": "license_id", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "currency_id", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "product_service_pricing_id", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "software_pricing_id", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "dom_pricing_id", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "parent_cart_id", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "cart_item_id", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "payment_gateway", "value": "0" }
  ],
